TCP - Makes sure data is either fully delivered or not delivered
DNS - Domain name System

Validator.w3.org  for validating webpages

action tag - helps with landing pages

forms --- autocomplete = off , autofocus 

select tag in form is used for the  dropdown menu  option

datalist tag is used to create a list and autocompletes your options when filling them..remember you have to specify the list in the input tag and should correspomd with the datalist id 

the > is used to select the direct child elements inside of a tag 

Page responsiveness
You can use the display flex and wrap or
you can divide the div to columns using bootstrap's row and column feature, this divides the page to a total of 12 divisions the column number  can differ so long as it sums up to 12